snippet.title: The Hour of Reckoning: A Thanksgiving Message "I Had A Choice"!
snippet.description: Hope is like faith, which is groping in the dark with courage and determination even when we cannot ascertain what is awaiting us in the dark tunnel ahead. Southern Cameroonians aka Ambazonians are today at the crossroads of history as we struggle to know who is truly for us from those who are wolves in sheep clothing in our midst. Falsehood appears to have a huge appeal, as numbers make sense when they sooth some, and become anathema when they are against them. The hour today is that of truth: we must come to the clear understanding that despite its popular appeal, falsehood and manipulation can never be the path to embrace in the pursuit of freedom when the objective is to set up a just and egalitarian nation. Watch, share, and subscribe.
